# Observability — <%= appName %>

Structured logging (Pino), OpenTelemetry tracing, and a basic `/metrics` endpoint.

## Environment

```env
LOG_LEVEL=info
OTEL_SERVICE_NAME=<%= appName %>
OTEL_EXPORTER_OTLP_ENDPOINT=http://localhost:4318
```

## Usage

```typescript
import { logger, startTelemetry, registerMetricsPlugin } from './src/platform/observability/index.js';

startTelemetry();
logger.info('Server starting');
await registerMetricsPlugin(app);
```
